title: Svenja Huth - Wikipedia
snippet: In 2019, Huth moved to VfL Wolfsburg. In 2020 she won the German Championship and the DFB Cup with Wolfsburg. In 2021, the cup was defended with a 1–0 win after extra time against Eintracht Frankfurt.

title: Kapitänin verlängert | VfL Wolfsburg
